rman''|Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster}}\n| Warner Bros. / Legendary Pictures / Syncopy\n| $225&nbsp;million\n| $668&nbsp;million\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2016\n| ''[[Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice]]''\n| Zack Snyder\n| [[Chris Terrio]] and David S. Goyer\n| {{Based on|''Batman''|Bob Kane with Bill Finger}}<br />{{Based on|''Superman''|Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster}}\n| Warner Bros. / [[RatPac-Dune Entertainment|RatPac Entertainment]] / [[Atlas Entertainment]] / [[Cruel and Unusual Films]]\n| $250&nbsp;million\n| $873.6&nbsp;million\n|-\n| ''[[Suicide Squad (film)|Suicide Squad]]''\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[David Ayer]]\n| {{based on|''[[Suicide Squad]]''|[[John Ostrander]]}}\n| Warner Bros. / RatPac Entertainment / Atlas Entertainment\n| $175&nbsp;million\n| $746.8&nbsp;million<ref name=\"Suicide Squad grossed $700 million\">{{cite web |title=Suicide Squad grossed $700&nbsp;million |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=dc2016.htm |access-date=September 12, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128062842/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=dc2016.htm |archive-date=January 28, 2017 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=3|2017\n| ''[[The Lego Batman Movie]]''\n| [[Chris McKay]]\n| '''Story by''' [[Seth Grahame-Smith]]<br />'''Screenplay by''' [[Seth Grahame-Smith]], [[Chris McKenna (writer)|Chris McKenna]] & Erik Sommers, Jared Stern & John Whittington\n| {{based on|''Batman''|Bob Kane with Bill Finger}}\n| Warner Bros. / [[The Lego Group|LEGO System A/S]] / [[Warner Bros. Animation|Warner Animation Group]] / [[RatPac Entertainment]] / [[Dan Lin|Lin Pictures]] / [[Phil Lord and Christopher Miller|Lord Miller Productions]] / [[Vertigo Entertainment]]\n| $80&nbsp;million<ref>{{cite web|title=The Lego Batman Movie (2017)|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=lego2.htm|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=February 11, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216043409/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=lego2.htm|archive-date=Fe