/the_dark_knight/ |title=The Dark Knight |date=July 18, 2008 |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=August 17, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224211913/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_dark_knight/ |archive-date=February 24, 2014 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| 82 (39 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-dark-knight |title=The Dark Knight |publisher=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=September 22, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209142618/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-dark-knight |archive-date=February 9, 2014 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|A}}\n|-\n| ''Watchmen''\n| 64% (305 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/watchmen/ |title=Watchmen |date=March 6, 2009 |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=August 17, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140916115359/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/watchmen/ |archive-date=September 16, 2014 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| 56 (39 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/watchmen |title=Watchmen |publisher=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=September 22, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100821105512/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/watchmen |archive-date=August 21, 2010 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|B}}\n|-\n| ''Jonah Hex''\n| 12% (149 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jonah_hex/ |title=Jonah Hex |date=June 18, 2010 |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=August 17, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017043849/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jonah_hex/ |archive-date=October 17, 2014 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| 33 (32 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/jonah-hex |title=Jonah Hex |publisher=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=September 22, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215121503/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/jonah-hex |archive-date=December 15, 2014 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| {{sort grade