tic]] |accessdate=September 22, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706192545/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/man-of-steel |archive-date=July 6, 2014 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|A\u2212}}\n|-\n| ''Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice''\n| 28% (411 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_v_superman_dawn_of_justice/ |title=Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |date=March 19, 2016 |accessdate=August 17, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602154520/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_v_superman_dawn_of_justice |archive-date=June 2, 2017 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| 44 (51 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice |title=Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice |publisher=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=March 26, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329082241/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice |archive-date=March 29, 2016 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|B}}\n|-\n| ''Suicide Squad''\n| 27% (362 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/suicide_squad_2016/ |title=Suicide Squad |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |date=August 1, 2016 |accessdate=August 17, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914214209/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/suicide_squad_2016/ |archive-date=September 14, 2016 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| 40 (53 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/suicide-squad |title=Suicide Squad |publisher=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=August 5, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806112449/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/suicide-squad |archive-date=August 6, 2016 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|B+}}\n|-\n| ''The Lego Batman Movie''\n| 90% (301 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_lego_batman_movie |title=The Lego Batman Movie |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |date=January 29, 